                incorrect: (v) => `Not quite! ${v.mysteryAngle}° is **${v.mysteryType}** because it's ${v.mysteryReason}. Remember: acute < 90°, right = 90°, obtuse is 91°-179°, straight = 180°, reflex > 180°.`
